00:36:04.090 --> 00:36:06.260
And I enjoy that.

00:36:06.260 --> 00:36:06.760
I really do.

00:36:06.760 --> 00:36:08.384
PHILLIP KNOLL: Yes,
so I guess that was

00:36:08.384 --> 00:36:09.520
