00:36:09.520 --> 00:36:09.990
NATHAN ALBERT: A follow up?

00:36:09.990 --> 00:36:10.580
PHILLIP KNOLL: A follow up, yes.

00:36:10.580 --> 00:36:13.220
So you said people had
questioned your own sexuality,

00:36:13.220 --> 00:36:15.500
not just because you were
involved in musical theater,

00:36:15.500 --> 00:36:17.360
